        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家有意，命人将他请来，月下相谈，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这命何人去请？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你去请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得了晓得了。哎呀呀，不去了，不去了，我不去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏为何去而复返？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是我去而复返，倘若老夫人知道，那时我定讨没趣，我才不去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我本是姑表亲必真不假，"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老夫人她知道大理不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有张生戏莺莺西厢月下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "穿针的小红娘就是奴家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "将身儿坐在了西厢月下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "等表兄他到来细说根芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子、丫鬟同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷请吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今夜晚夜明灯竹簾高挂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫我读书人喜在心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "彩屏姐你不走所为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这里正行走用目观看"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要走了，来到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着，待我与你通禀一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓，你与我通禀一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀小姐：解元爷到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说我这里有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她倒不出来了。待我自己进去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，解元爷不用请，他自己进来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎彩屏姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏过来，对他说道，我这里修书不及，未完花烛，还是姑表兄妹相称。叫他"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "稳重些。还要往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎解元爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，彩屏姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家姑娘说道，修书不及，未完花烛，还是姑表兄妹相称。叫你放稳重些，还"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，叫我往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还要往下站。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，还要往下站，哦哦哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见表妹说的是真情实话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫我大张口无有话答。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "况且那我也是宦门根芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "她本是千金女必真不假"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏与解元爷看坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有坐。请问表妹，一向可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何德能，敢劳表兄动问，请问表兄可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳表妹承问。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问表兄，几时入场赴试？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今天十四，明天十五，就是我入场之日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此去可得会元？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然不得中，不落于人后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个虽然不得中，不落于人后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏过来，花园之中，姑娘未带什么含心之物，带来明月珠一颗，送与解元爷"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带进场去，文章不中，宝上便取。来来来，付珠过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷，我家姑娘言道：花园之中，未带什么含心之物，今有明月珠一颗，赠"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与解元爷带进场去，文章不中，宝上便取。来来来，付珠过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏姐，观见此宝明晃闪闪，日后必中花中之连。彩屏姐，就说我谢赠珠之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷，谢过小姐赠珠之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩屏对我表兄说道：叫他回到东亭书馆安身，明天好去得中花中之连。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷，我家姑娘言道：请回东亭书馆安身，明天好去得中魁元。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就说我告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐奉送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "解元爷只生得十分好看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "赛过了小潘郎那等容颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见表妹只生得十分好看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一霎时引得我骨软酥麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "解元爷只生得难描难画，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元爷吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我姑娘只生得闭月羞花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿得我表兄鱼龙变化，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小姐下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "准备着三杯酒帽插宫花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "恨不能将表妹搂抱在怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "适才间与表妹一同讲话"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "解元爷你不要心慌意乱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "要完婚除非是头带乌纱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立妆台遇佳人，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解元此去跳龙门。我姑娘绣阁常在耳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "准备红花报好音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个“准备红花报好音”。"
        }
      ],
